[This spillover event is the 3rd outbreak in 2 years. This represents a rapid rate of emergence of Ebola virus from its sylvatic reservoir(s). Such a high rate of emergence underlines the importance of studying the sylvatic and farmed vertebrate hosts and, equally, maintaining a strong public health infrastructure that is ready to respond immediately upon detection of new cases.

See source URL for all references and figures. - Mod.LK

